        {
            "id": 6124491,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 兆聯實業(6944)股價拉至漲停，漲停價595.0元，成交877張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>兆聯實業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6944:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6944\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6944-TW</a>)25日10:06上漲54元，股價漲停報595.0元，委買5張、委賣234張，成交877張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為高科技廠房純水﹑廢水回收系統工程及維運。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>兆聯實業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6944:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6944\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6944-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲8.2%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌2.34%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,031 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+610 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+439 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-18 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6124491",
